---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Services
description: Managed IT, cloud, network security, backup & recovery, remote support, compliance, and VoIP — one accountable team with flat monthly pricing.
permalink: /services/
ctaHeading: "Not sure which services you need?"
ctaSub: "Book a free 30-minute consult and we'll map your risks and gaps — no jargon."
---

<section class="section" style="padding-bottom:24px; background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--mist-50),#fff); text-align:center;" aria-label="Services overview">
  <span class="pill">What we do</span>
  <h1 class="display-1" style="max-width:820px; margin:18px auto 0;">A complete IT department, managed for you</h1>
  <p class="lead" style="max-width:640px; margin:20px auto 0;">Seven core services, one accountable team, and flat monthly pricing built for the compliance demands of healthcare, legal, and financial firms.</p>
</section>

<nav class="chip-row" aria-label="Jump to a service">
  {% for svc in services.items %}
  <a class="chip" href="#{{ svc.id }}">{{ svc.chip }}</a>
  {% endfor %}
</nav>

{% for svc in services.items %}
<section id="{{ svc.id }}" class="split{% if loop.index is even %} split--mist split--flip{% endif %}" aria-labelledby="{{ svc.id }}-heading">
  <div>
    <p class="split__index">{{ svc.index }}</p>
    <h2 id="{{ svc.id }}-heading">{{ svc.heading }}</h2>
    <p class="body-copy">{{ svc.body }}</p>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      {% for f in svc.features %}
      <li>{{ f }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
  {% if svc.image %}
  <img class="photo" src="{{ svc.image }}" alt="{{ svc.imageLabel }}" style="min-height:340px">
  {% else %}
  <div class="img-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder image: {{ svc.imageLabel }}">
    <span>[ image &mdash; {{ svc.imageLabel }} ]</span>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</section>
{% endfor %}

{% if site.sections.industries %}
<section class="section section--navy" id="industries" aria-labelledby="svc-industries-heading">
  <div class="section-head">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--light">Who we serve</p>
    <h2 id="svc-industries-heading" class="display-2" style="font-size:clamp(28px,3vw,36px)">Tailored to regulated industries</h2>
  </div>
  {% set indCount = industries.items | length %}
  <div class="grid-industries{% if indCount <= 4 %} grid-industries--{{ indCount }}{% endif %}">
    {% for ind in industries.items %}
    <div class="industry-card">
      <div class="industry-card__index">{{ ind.label }}</div>
      <h3>{{ ind.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ ind.body }}</p>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% include "partials/cta.njk" %}
